name: Here we go again (Propelar)
description:
Here we go again!

Simple and fun 2D Platformer!

Can you collect all the cherries and magic gems?

Game includes:

- 2 Different Difficulties

- A variety of enemies

- Collectible cherries

- Special magic gems

How to download (optional):

- Download the zip file

- Extract its content

- Open "ante pali"

- Play

Controls:

- Move: [A] [D] or [Left arrow] [Right arrow]

- Jump: [W] or [Spacebar]

- That's it  ._.

Objectives:

- Collect all cherries

- Collect all magic gems

- Finish the game in each difficulty

Credits to ansimuz for the art!

Have fun!
